\section introduction Introduction

The <a href="http://www.dune-project.org">%DUNE</a> module <tt>dune-spgrid</tt>
provides a structured, parallel grid (\ref Dune::SPGrid "SPGrid").
Though the <tt>dune-grid</tt> module already contains two structured grids,
<tt>SGrid</tt> and <tt>YaspGrid</tt>, both lack several important features
(see \ref features for details).


